snippet.textDisplay:
Seriously very disappointed season so far, each song has a different music director and that ruins it. Rohail hyatt was doing great in those first 6 seasons, strings came into scene after him and, they were doing fairly good after rohail hyatt, but now this new experiment of one song per music director ruins every thing.
Coke Studio Pakistan needs its old format, either strings or rohail hyatt.
